"title": "5414: money, stewardship of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5414: money, stewardship of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The righteous handling of money is an important practical test of godliness.</p>\n<h2>Money must be obtained honestly</h2>\n<h3>Not by theft</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:15\">EXO 20:15</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:19\">DEU 5:19</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:2\">PRO 10:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:26\">PRO 19:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:19\">MRK 10:19</a></p>\n<h3>Not by fraudulent practices</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:13\">LEV 19:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:1\">PRO 11:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:11\">PRO 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:10\">PRO 20:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:18\">EZK 28:18</a></p>\n<h3>Not by usury</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:25\">EXO 22:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps15:5\">PSA 15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:8\">PRO 28:8</a></p>\n<h3>Not at the expense of justice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:8\">EXO 23:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:27\">PRO 15:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:8\">PRO 16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:11\">JER 17:11</a></p>\n<h3>Not by extortion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:13\">LUK 3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:12\">EZK 22:12</a></p>\n<h3>Not by oppression</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:4\">JAS 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:16\">PRO 22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:7-Ezek18:8\">EZK 18:7–18:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:11\">AMO 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:5\">MAL 3:5</a></p>\n<h3>Not at the expense of health</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:4\">PRO 23:4</a></p>\n<h3>Not at the expense of witness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:22-Gen14:23\">GEN 14:22–14:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:7\">3JN 1:7</a></p>\n<h3>Not at the expense of spiritual well-being</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:26\">MAT 16:26</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:36\">MRK 8:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:25\">LUK 9:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:16–12:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:9\">1TI 6:9</a></p>\n<h3>By work, trade, investment or inheritance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:12\">2TH 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:2\">GEN 15:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:21\">GEN 34:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:11\">PRO 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:22\">PRO 13:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:23\">PRO 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:14\">PRO 19:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:27\">MAT 25:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:23\">LUK 19:23</a></p>\n<h2>Money must be cared for diligently</h2>\n<h3>Personal money</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:23-Prov27:24\">PRO 27:23–27:24</a></p>\n<h3>Money held on trust</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:4-2Kgs22:7\">2KI 22:4–22:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:14-Matt25:27\">MAT 25:14–25:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:10-Luke16:12\">LUK 16:10–16:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:2\">1CO 4:2</a></p>\n<h2>Money must be used in a God-honouring way</h2>\n<h3>For the support of the family</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:8\">1TI 5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:16\">1TI 5:16</a></p>\n<h3>For benefiting the poor, especially God's people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:10\">GAL 6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:17\">PRO 19:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:27\">PRO 28:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:3-Matt6:4\">MAT 6:3–6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:33\">LUK 12:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:29\">JHN 13:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:45\">ACT 2:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:26\">ROM 15:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:10\">GAL 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:18\">1TI 6:18</a></p>\n<h3>For the work of God's kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:6\">GAL 6:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:9-Prov3:10\">PRO 3:9–3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:10\">MAL 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:3\">LUK 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:9\">LUK 16:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:14-Phil4:19\">PHP 4:14–4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:17-1Tim5:18\">1TI 5:17–5:18</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of godly people who have used their money well</h2>\n<h3>Those who were wealthy but godly</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:2\">GEN 13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:14\">GEN 26:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:43\">GEN 30:43</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:32\">2SA 19:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:22\">2CH 9:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:3\">JOB 1:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:57\">MAT 27:57</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:34-Acts4:36\">ACT 4:34–4:36</a></p>\n<h3>Those who had little but gave much</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:41-Mark12:44\">MRK 12:41–12:44</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:1-Luke21:4\">LUK 21:1–21:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:1-2Cor8:4\">2CO 8:1–8:4</a></p>",
